edu.iu.dsc.tws.data.memory

Class OperationMemoryManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iu.dsc.tws.data.memory.OperationMemoryManager

  • public class OperationMemoryManager
extends java.lang.Object
    This controls the memory manager for a single operation. An example of an operation is a gather, reduce. Note: This class needs to implment all the methods in the Memory Manager interface without the operationID parameter

    TODO: We can latter look into making the operation manager typed. Based on the messageType TODO: Then the get methods such as the iterator can directly return the typed objects
